"title": "5746: youth",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5746: youth",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture characterises youth as a time of vigour and strength. It speaks, too, of the pressures and expectations of youth, warns about the temptations facing young people, and instructs the young about what is expected of them.</p>\n<h2>The vigour of youth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:29\">PRO 20:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:25\">JOB 33:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:5\">PSA 103:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:12\">PSA 144:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:3\">SNG 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:9-Eccl11:10\">ECC 11:9–11:10</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:30\">ISA 40:30</a></strong> <em>Even youthful strength and vigour may fail.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:11\">JOB 20:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:31\">PSA 78:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:13\">AMO 8:13</a></p>\n<h2>The duties of youth</h2>\n<h3>To remember God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:1\">ECC 12:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:12\">1KI 18:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:5\">PSA 71:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:25-Lam3:27\">LAM 3:25–3:27</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:9\">PSA 119:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:17\">PSA 71:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:14\">EZK 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>To respect the elderly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:32\">LEV 19:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:8\">JOB 29:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job32:6\">JOB 32:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:1\">1TI 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a></p>\n<h3>To honour parents</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:12\">EXO 20:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:16\">DEU 5:16</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:2-Eph6:3\">EPH 6:2–6:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:3\">LEV 19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:4\">1TI 5:4</a></p>\n<h3>To obey parents</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:8\">PRO 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:20\">PRO 6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:22\">PRO 23:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:1\">EPH 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:20\">COL 3:20</a></p>\n<h3>To remain faithful to one's partner</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:18\">PRO 5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:17\">PRO 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:14-Mal2:15\">MAL 2:14–2:15</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of godly young people</h2>\n<h3>Godly young men</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:18\">1SA 2:18</a> <em>Samuel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:33\">1SA 17:33</a> <em>David, fighting Goliath</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:1-2Chr24:2\">2CH 24:1–24:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:1-2Kgs12:2\">2KI 12:1–12:2</a> <em>Joash became king at the age of seven</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:1-2Chr34:2\">2CH 34:1–34:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:1-2Kgs22:2\">2KI 22:1–22:2</a> <em>Josiah became king at the age of eight</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:42-Luke2:52\">LUK 2:42–2:52</a> <em>Jesus Christ at the age of twelve</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:5\">2TI 1:5</a> <em>Timothy</em></p>\n<h3>Godly young women</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:36\">JDG 11:36</a> <em>Jephthah's daughter</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:16-Ruth1:17\">RUT 1:16–1:17</a> <em>Ruth</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:15-Esth4:16\">EST 4:15–4:16</a> <em>Esther</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:38\">LUK 1:38</a> <em>the virgin Mary</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:9\">ACT 21:9</a> <em>Philip's daughters</em></p>\n<h2>The promise of youth</h2>\n<h3>Israel's youthful devotion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:2\">JER 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:4\">JER 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:22\">EZK 16:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:43\">EZK 16:43</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:14-Hos2:15\">HOS 2:14–2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:4\">ISA 54:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:5\">ISA 62:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:60\">EZK 16:60</a></p>\n<h3>Dying young as a sign of judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:45\">PSA 89:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:14\">JOB 36:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:63\">PSA 78:63</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:12\">ISA 13:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:21\">JER 9:21</a> <em>The death of children and young people symbolises loss of hope for the future</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:22\">JER 11:22</a></p>\n<h2>Particular pressures of youth</h2>\n<h3>The inexperience of youth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:7\">1KI 3:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:5\">1CH 22:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:1\">1CH 29:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr13:7\">2CH 13:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:6\">JER 1:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:12\">1TI 4:12</a></p>\n<h3>Temptations facing the young</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:22\">2TI 2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:7\">PRO 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:13\">LUK 15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:30\">LUK 15:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:22\">MAT 19:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:22\">MRK 10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:23\">LUK 18:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:6\">TIT 2:6</a></p>\n<h3>Troubles faced from the time of one's youth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:7\">2SA 19:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:15\">PSA 88:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps129:1-Ps129:2\">PSA 129:1–129:2</a></p>\n<h2>The sins of youth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:7\">PSA 25:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job13:26\">JOB 13:26</a></p>\n<h3>Disrespect for older people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:23-2Kgs2:24\">2KI 2:23–2:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:1\">JOB 30:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:5\">ISA 3:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:12\">LAM 5:12</a></p>\n<h3>Dishonouring parents</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:18-Deut21:20\">DEU 21:18–21:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:20\">PRO 15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:11\">PRO 30:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:2\">2TI 3:2</a></p>\n<h3>Persistent sinfulness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:24-Jer3:25\">JER 3:24–3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:21\">JER 22:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:30\">JER 32:30</a></p>\n<h3>The sinfulness of Israel's youth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:3\">EZK 23:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:8\">EZK 23:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:19-Ezek23:21\">EZK 23:19–23:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1-Hos11:2\">HOS 11:1–11:2</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of sinful young men</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:17\">1SA 2:17</a> <em>the sons of Eli</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:2-1Sam8:3\">1SA 8:2–8:3</a> <em>the sons of Samuel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:6\">2SA 15:6</a> <em>Absalom</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:8-1Kgs12:14\">1KI 12:8–12:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:8-2Chr10:11\">2CH 10:8–10:11</a> <em>Rehoboam</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:1-2Kgs21:2\">2KI 21:1–21:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:1-2Chr33:2\">2CH 33:1–33:2</a> <em>Manasseh</em></p>",
